transcripts.text: One in every three people resident in my county town of Longford is non-national, as is the case of my local town of Edgartstown.
Your policies of mass immigration are ruining towns like Edgerton and Lord Arran.  Sorry, sir, we don't have a policy of mass immigration.  You have.

They want a new plantation to fill this country with foreign nationals, to bring about a multicultural dispensation in this country, and to make the Irish a minority in their own country.  That's the new plantation policy.
